  <brief_title>Effects of Remifentanil on Respiratory Function in Mechanically Ventilated Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Remifentanil on Breathing Pattern, Respiratory Effort and Gas Exchange in Mechanically Ventilated Patients.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
